race.comment: SKATING ON BY (11) looks well placed here. Former Victorian who resumed in town at first run for the new yard and gave a sight, just missing the frame when fourth in a 50k race. Fitter and surely hard to beat this line-up. STARS ARE ALIGNING (12) is having first run for a new yard. Returns from a long break but has run a decent race when fresh and looks well placed here. ALLROUNDGOODGUY (1) raced on speed and faded on a wet track at the provincials, fresh from a break. Strips fitter and should be around the mark. POWER PRIMO (10) finished off last campaign here at the end of last season with a fourth. Locally trained given a good spell and has run well fresh. Must include. ARLO'S DREAM (2) is another resuming from a long break. Has some fresh form and worth keeping safe.
